{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_mkd_004233",ch="mkd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"真琴"},
"「だったら、これって……」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00186",
linknext="block_00188",
},
block_00188={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rnd_004230",ch="rnd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"稟"},
"「たぶん、なおくんが、ここに立った瞬間に思いついたんだと思う」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00187",
linknext="block_00189",
},
block_00189={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_mkd_004234",ch="mkd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"真琴"},
"「立った瞬間？」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00188",
linknext="block_00190",
},
block_00190={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rnd_004231",ch="rnd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"稟"},
"「最初に立った時……、『櫻達の足跡』を完成させる以前」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00189",
linknext="block_00191",
},
block_00191={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_mkd_004235",ch="mkd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"真琴"},
"「あの作品を完成させる以前って……」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00190",
linknext="block_00192",
},
block_00192={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_mkd_004236",ch="mkd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"真琴"},
"「でも、これは思いつきだけで出来るもんじゃないわ。日周運動とかいろいろと難しいハズだし」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00191",
linknext="block_00193",
},
block_00193={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rnd_004232",ch="rnd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"稟"},
"「そうね。だから、たぶんずっと考えてたんだと思う」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00192",
linknext="block_00194",
},
block_00194={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rnd_004233",ch="rnd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"稟"},
"「この場に立って、草薙健一郎の作品を夢想して、自分ならば、何が出来るか？　それ以上のものは出来るのか？　ってね」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00193",
linknext="block_00195",
},
block_00195={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rnd_004234",ch="rnd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"稟"},
"「これ以外の方法も……いろいろ考えていたのだと思う」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00194",
linknext="block_00196",
},
block_00196={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_mkd_004237",ch="mkd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"真琴"},
"「これ以外の方法？」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00195",
linknext="block_00197",
},
block_00197={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rnd_004235",ch="rnd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"稟"},
"「日周運動をいくら計算して、時間を合わせたところで、季節が大幅にずれれば、このステンドグラスを太陽は通過しない」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00196",
linknext="block_00198",
},
block_00198={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rnd_004236",ch="rnd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"稟"},
"「なおくんって、いろいろな事にクビを突っ込んで、いろいろなアイディアをすぐに出す様に見えるけど、違うんだよ」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00197",
linknext="block_00199",
},
block_00199={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rnd_004237",ch="rnd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"稟"},
"「あれはね。全部長い時間、それこそ無限とも思える思考の連続によって生み出されたものばかり……」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00198",
linknext="block_00200",
},
block_00200={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rnd_004238",ch="rnd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"稟"},
"「夏目圭くん。草薙健一郎さん。そして私。たぶん、これらの人間が作品を発表するたびに、彼は研究して、自分だったら何が出来るかを探っている……」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00199",
linknext="block_00201",
},
block_00201={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rnd_004239",ch="rnd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"稟"},
"「あの人の中には数え切れないほどのアイディアがあり、そしてそれを具現化出来る技術もある」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00200",
linknext="block_00202",
},
block_00202={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_mkd_004238",ch="mkd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"真琴"},
"「でも、何も発表してない」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00201",
linknext="block_00203",
},
block_00203={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rnd_004240",ch="rnd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"稟"},
"「あれから何年経ったかな……」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00202",
linknext="block_00204",
},
block_00204={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rnd_004241",ch="rnd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"稟"},
"「まだ、なおくんの中で炎は燃え続けている……」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00203",
linknext="block_00205",
},
block_00205={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rnd_004242",ch="rnd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"稟"},
"「だから、私は行かなければならない……」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00204",
linknext="block_00206",
},
block_00206={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rnd_004243",ch="rnd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"稟"},
"「私では行けない場所……、約束された地点……」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00205",
linknext="block_00207",
},
block_00207={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rnd_004244",ch="rnd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"稟"},
"「まこちゃん」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00206",
linknext="block_00208",
},
block_00208={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_mkd_004239",ch="mkd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"真琴"},
"「何？」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00207",
linknext="block_00209",
},
block_00209={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rnd_004245",ch="rnd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"稟"},
"「最後、私となおくんが会った時に、彼はこんな事を言った……」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00208",
linknext="block_00210",
},
block_00210={
{"bg",file="ev_com_j08_02",sync=0,face=1,time=400,path=":ev/ev_com_j08/",set="ev_com_j08"},
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rnd_004246",ch="rnd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"稟"},
"「I dwell in Possibility―",
{"rt2"},
"私は可能性のなかに住んでいる」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00209",
linknext="block_00211",
},
block_00211={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rnd_004247",ch="rnd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"稟"},
"「A fairer House than Prose―",
{"rt2"},
"散文より立派な家に」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00210",
linknext="block_00212",
},
block_00212={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rnd_004248",ch="rnd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"稟"},
"「More numerous of Windows―",
{"rt2"},
"窓かずもずっと多く」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00211",
linknext="block_00213",
},
block_00213={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rnd_004249",ch="rnd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"稟"},
"「Superior―for Doors―",
{"rt2"},
"戸も一層すぐれている」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00212",
linknext="block_00214",
},
block_00214={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rnd_004250",ch="rnd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"稟"},
"「Of Chambers as the Cedars―",
{"rt2"},
"それぞれの部屋には」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00213",
linknext="block_00215",
},
block_00215={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rnd_004251",ch="rnd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"稟"},
"「Impregnable of Eye―",
{"rt2"},
"目も侵せない西洋杉」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00214",
linknext="block_00216",
},
block_00216={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rnd_004252",ch="rnd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"稟"},
"「And for an Everlasting Roof",
{"rt2"},
"The Gambrels of the Sky―」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00215",
linknext="block_00217",
},
block_00217={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rnd_004253",ch="rnd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"稟"},
"「永遠の屋根には",
{"rt2"},
"空の切妻屋根――」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00216",
linknext="block_00218",
},
block_00218={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rnd_004254",ch="rnd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"稟"},
"「Of Visitors―the fairest―",
{"rt2"},
"訪問者は美しいひとびとだけ」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00217",
linknext="block_00219",
},
block_00219={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rnd_004255",ch="rnd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"稟"},
"「For Occupation―This―",
{"rt2"},
"そしてわたしの仕事は」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00218",
linknext="block_00220",
},
block_00220={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rnd_004256",ch="rnd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"稟"},
"「The spreading wide my narrow Hands",
{"rt2"},
"To gather Paradise―」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00219",
linknext="block_00221",
},
block_00221={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rnd_004257",ch="rnd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"稟"},
"「この小さい手をいっぱい広げて",
{"rt2"},
"天国をつかむこと」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00220",
linknext="block_00222",
},
block_00222={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rnd_004258",ch="rnd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"稟"},
"「当時は、その言葉は私自身に向けられたものだと思っていた……」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00221",
linknext="block_00223",
},
block_00223={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rnd_004259",ch="rnd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"稟"},
"「けど……」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00222",
linknext="block_00224",
},
block_00224={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_szd_001938",ch="szd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"雫"},
"「稟……そろそろ時間」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00223",
linknext="block_00225",
},
block_00225={
{"bg",file="ev_com_j08_01",sync=0,face=1,time=400,path=":ev/ev_com_j08/",set="ev_com_j08"},
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rnd_004260",ch="rnd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"稟"},
"「うん、そうだね」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00224",
linknext="block_00226",
},
block_00226={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_mkd_004240",ch="mkd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"真琴"},
"「また、日本に戻ってくるの？」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00225",
linknext="block_00227",
},
block_00227={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rnd_004261",ch="rnd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"稟"},
"「たぶん……」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00226",
linknext="block_00228",
},
block_00228={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_mkd_004241",ch="mkd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"真琴"},
"「その時は、みんなに会ってくれるんだよね」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00227",
linknext="block_00229",
},
block_00229={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rnd_004262",ch="rnd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"稟"},
"「うん」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00228",
linknext="block_00230",
},
block_00230={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_mkd_004242",ch="mkd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"真琴"},
"「稟……」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00229",
linknext="block_00231",
},
block_00231={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rnd_004265",ch="rnd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"稟"},
"「だから、今日はありがとう」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00230",
linknext="block_00232",
},
block_00232={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rnd_004266",ch="rnd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"稟"},
"「昔の友達として、最後に接してくれて……」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00231",
linknext="block_00233",
},
block_00233={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_szd_001939",ch="szd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"雫"},
"「もう時間」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00232",
linknext="block_00234",
},
block_00234={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rnd_004267",ch="rnd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"稟"},
"「んじゃ、またね」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00233",
linknext="block_00235",
},
